 cấp nhưng bạn cũng cần lưu ý kiểm tra một cách kỹ lưỡng nhé.</p><div tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-cke-widget-wrapper=\"1\" data-cke-filter=\"off\" class=\"cke_widget_wrapper cke_widget_block cke_widget_image\" data-cke-display-name=\"ảnh\" data-cke-widget-id=\"7\" role=\"region\" aria-label=\" ảnh widget\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><figure class=\"image cke_widget_element\" data-cke-widget-keep-attr=\"0\" data-widget=\"image\" data-cke-widget-data=\"%7B%22hasCaption%22%3Atrue%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbenhviendongho.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FUlysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03-1024x689.jpg%22%2C%22alt%22%3A%22%22%2C%22width%22%3A%22700%22%2C%22height%22%3A%22471%22%2C%22lock%22%3Atrue%2C%22align%22%3A%22center%22%2C%22classes%22%3A%7B%7D%7D\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"><span class=\"cke_image_resizer_wrapper\"><img data-cke-saved-src=\"https://benhviendongho.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ulysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03-1024x689.jpg\" src=\"https://benhviendongho.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ulysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03-1024x689.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"471\" srcset=\"https://benhviendongho.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ulysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03.jpg 1024w, https://benhviendongho.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ulysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03-300x202.jpg 300w, https://benhviendongho.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ulysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03-768x517.jpg 768w, https://benhviendongho.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Ulysse-Nardin-Grand-Deck-Marine-Tourbillon-Timepiece-03-600x404.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" data-cke-widget-upcasted=\"1\"><span class=\"cke_image_resizer\" title=\"Kéo rê để thay đổi kích cỡ\">​</span></span><figcaption contenteditable=\"true\" data-cke-widget-editable=\"caption\" data-cke-enter-mode=\"2\" data-cke-filt